#url /datasources
#type operation
#method get
#description Returns a list of data sources matching the given filters. Note: OpenCitations does not currently hold data source records; this endpoint always returns an empty result.
#custom_params filter,handle_skgif_datasource_filter,preprocess,Search filter.
Format: comma-separated <code>filter_name:filter_value</code> pairs (AND logic).
<br><br>
<strong>Accepted but always empty (OpenCitations does not hold data source records):</strong>
<ul>
  <li><code>acronym</code></li>
  <li><code>cf.search.name</code></li>
  <li><code>data_source_classification</code></li>
  <li><code>identifiers.scheme</code></li>
  <li><code>identifiers.value</code></li>
  <li><code>research_product_type</code></li>
</ul>
